18 dps x 30 secs = 540 dmg/pet (as it works now)<br>
18 dps x 60 secs = 1080 dmg/pet (as it should work, described by the AA skill)<br>
<br>
540 dmg x 5 pets (level 1) = 2700 dmg.<br>
540 dmg x 7 pets (level 2) = 3780 dmg.<br>
540 dmg x 9 pets (level 3) = 4860 dmg.<br>
<br>
1080 dmg x 5 pets (level 1) = 5400 dmg.<br>
1080 dmg x 7 pets (level 2) = 7560 dmg.<br>
1080 dmg x 9 pets (level 3) = 9720 dmg.<br>
<br>
Keep in mind that these mini pets, if they lasted 60 seconds, would be subject to AE, rampage, attacked by adds, positioning, pet's popping due to pathing, and all the other issues that plague normal pets.<br>
<br>
And please, let's not hear any comparisons to Manaburn.  Totally different issues.  That's like comparing Firebolt of Tallon to Garrison's Superior Sundering, when one is a Bolt plagued by issues and the other is a DD.  People seem to forget about that. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style=""><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=59365">Kathodos</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Battle Cleric of Tunare - Tholuxe Paells</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style=""><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=59365">Kantreach</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Arch Mage Antagonist - Tholuxe Paells</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=h0gfather>H0gfather</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 650<br> <font color=#333333>(10/31/02 4:17:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=421.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.aus-1.au.nu/images/photo.gif width=90 height=112></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Host of the Elements - useful and fun i say :)</span><hr size=1> OK before someone says it, there is no valid comparison to Manaburn. <br>
